'''Totally Games''' is a [[Wikipedia:video game developer|video game company]] based in [[Wikipedia:Marin County, California|Marin County]], [[Wikipedia:California|California]]. The company was incorporated by [[Lawrence Holland]] in [[1994]]. Totally Games is well known for developing the [[X-Wing series (computer games)|''X-Wing'' computer game series]] for [[LucasArts|LucasArts Entertainment Company]].

